The paper discusses a recommender system that uses deep learning techniques, which falls under the category of information retrieval (cs.IR). The use of neural networks also suggests that it could be categorized under machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also mentions natural language processing (NLP) as one of the areas where deep learning has been successful, which could place it under the sub-category of social and information networks (cs.SI) or computational linguistics (cs.CL).
